  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Dirty Tactics Toolbox pg. 24</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate illusion <strong>CL</strong> 7th</p><p><strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special weapon ability can be placed on only melee weapons. When a character wielding a <em>dazzling radiance</em> weapon uses the Dazzling Display feat, the weapon flashes in a burst of bright color. All creatures within 15 feet of the wielder who can see the display must attempt a DC 17 Fortitude save. Those who fail are blinded for 2 rounds and dazzled for an additional 1d4 rounds; those who succeed are instead dazzled for 1d4 rounds.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>color spray</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
